{"id": 2283, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都发现了哪些女反派的设定套路？", "description": "影视作品里男坏蛋作妖的理由不少，女人坏起来翻来覆去就那几件事（题图来自：iStock©️CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 2402, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180416170550Twm8OPRx9iyBVvQN.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-18T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 276736, "content": "消失的爱人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320830}, {"id": 278272, "content": "挤眉弄眼，婊里婊气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327426}, {"id": 276737, "content": "败在一个情字", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 277505, "content": "后来她觉醒了，于是我是他的介绍申请入党。然后她要跟我来一发，我拒绝了，我说，同志请自重，革命不是炒菜做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487377}, {"id": 282369, "content": "男二强行变渣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347784}, {"id": 276738, "content": "女配设定白富美且聪明，但一旦遇到关于女主和男主的问题时，做出的举动如一个智障。作者后妈的偏爱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320856}, {"id": 276739, "content": "很有能力 （但如果女主是弱鸡 弃剧）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163177}, {"id": 277251, "content": "反派死于话多\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293385}, {"id": 280583, "content": "参阅电影《猎杀星期一》中的Monday和《头号玩家》IOI公司女助手的形象。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315067}, {"id": 276744, "content": "厚重的黑色齐刘海！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814771}, {"id": 275990, "content": "多半是为了爱而变得疯魔，作出各种反常言行", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 275991, "content": "要么是冷艳性感的蛇蝎美人／要么是作妖的老女人", "image": null, "praise_count": 436, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 275992, "content": "多用来衬托女主的善良纯洁", "image": null, "praise_count": 184, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 275993, "content": "总要跟男主发生点纠葛，比如想办法利用or诱惑策反", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 278041, "content": "每一个成功的女人后面都有一群男人为她铺路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326677}, {"id": 276774, "content": "话题全是男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810373}, {"id": 276539, "content": "抓唐僧做丈夫\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770804}, {"id": 276540, "content": "现在影视剧里的第三者通常是其貌不扬但温柔体贴善解人意能在工作中支持男人的。做大了就开始暴露本性，吃相难看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319890}, {"id": 276541, "content": "话多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127109}, {"id": 281917, "content": "一开始还挺好的，然后他喜欢的人不喜欢他，额，一般这个他就是男主，而且男主刚刚好喜欢的是女主，嫉妒女主呀，然后就开始打击报复，走上不归路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345391}, {"id": 276542, "content": "TA不爱我", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136940}, {"id": 276543, "content": "虚荣", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002171}, {"id": 276544, "content": "缺乏安全感，精神失常( ‘-ωก̀ )", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002171}, {"id": 276545, "content": "多半是为了男人\n而且与其说是坏\n不如说是蠢", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120213}, {"id": 276801, "content": "被男主伤害过", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1321062}, {"id": 276546, "content": "绿茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677618}, {"id": 276547, "content": "都有自己的正义", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737718}, {"id": 276548, "content": "永远比女主美！", "image": null, "praise_count": 262, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209614}, {"id": 276549, "content": "开局智商爆表，失败全因话多", "image": null, "praise_count": 350, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122099}, {"id": 276806, "content": "可以由女主的超级好闺蜜变成超级女反派", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1321085}, {"id": 278342, "content": "这么说吧，冰雪奇缘里Elsa出来没多久我就觉得她可能是反派了。（尤其到了唱来踢狗那段）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215504}, {"id": 276551, "content": "对女主羡慕嫉妒恨，而且女主很蠢，被设定不得不嫉妒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938486}, {"id": 276552, "content": "都会仰头大笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253833}, {"id": 276553, "content": "在其他事上一般都比女主聪明，但是遇到女主就得智商下线……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423216}, {"id": 276556, "content": "以前各种被欺负，小时候被qj，被人冷落，被人误解，还有一个误解了后被撞大脑袋的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316978}, {"id": 276557, "content": "以前各种被欺负，小时候被qj，被人冷落，被人误解，还有一个误解了后被撞大脑袋的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316978}, {"id": 276559, "content": "颜值极高", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313975}, {"id": 276561, "content": "和女主都爱上男主，无论谁先出现，无论谁更美，男主永远只爱女主。forever。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319953}, {"id": 276562, "content": "无论是颜值才华还是家室都实力吊打女主，但偏偏就没有男主的爱，所以黑化癫狂了", "image": null, "praise_count": 368, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317781}, {"id": 276563, "content": "长得很好看，心计深沉，男一男二都不喜欢她，而且他一定有一个真心相待的人那就是男主", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319962}, {"id": 276564, "content": "心狠起来连亲妈都能下手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 276565, "content": "都是被情所伤走上不归路的女子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317246}, {"id": 276566, "content": "一出場就暴露身分，算計的很明顯", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319973}, {"id": 276567, "content": "角色要么是后妈要么是婆婆。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943839}, {"id": 276568, "content": "一般变成反派的原因都是男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930967}, {"id": 276570, "content": "嫉妒心作祟", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313317}, {"id": 276571, "content": "妖艳贱货\n               ―谷阿莫", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265233}, {"id": 276572, "content": "黑长直齐刘海", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265196}, {"id": 276573, "content": "不管男反派女反派\n都是死于话多︶︿︶", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319833}, {"id": 276574, "content": "种马文里，长的妖艳又美丽是全天下男人的垂涎对象，但从来对男人表示藐视，一遇到主角就觉得他和别人不一样，表示非君不嫁，引you主角。之前设定的清冷如水的人物形象全崩了，变得小女人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319967}]}